<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. I velah buh lakding tamtak a min ta ie,
 Amauhaw at dingin chieh in;
 Lalpan hun huh ina, Na hatna suong loin,
 Lalpa hatna chuh suong zel inla;
 Na chi theh kek ina, Lalpan hun huh ina,
 Kumsawt gam na tunpih theihna di'n,
 Na hatlai in semin, Lalpa hatna suong in.

[V2]
 2. Nasep loh ziekin tamtak chuh a bei mang ui,
 Lalpa hehpihte a bei zel;
 Amau panpih dingin na chieh dem?
 Panpih ding a ngai ui. A beihmang zawh kal un;
 Chieh in, chieh in, semin, Amau di'n ni a kiem,
 Thagau simsen loh beimang ding chuh;
 Hehpih lo hiel na him? Khat mai bek hun puiin.

[V3]
 3. Khawdak in, enviel in, tatna helo tehi,
 Lalpa'n A tatdawk a he puou;
 Muong takin a um ui,
 A pui dingin kuomah a um puou;
 Hukdampa a he puou,
 Amau haw pui dingin, Lalpa'n a hun deih hi;
 Bangtik leh Isu anga kunin, A Tanpau ahih he'n,
 A Lalna min pakin?</lyrics>
<title>LILIES</title>
<hymn_number>288</hymn_number>
</song>